  "title": "chore(deps): update dependency eslint-config-prettier to v2.7.0",
  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier\">eslint-config-prettier</a> from <code>v2.6.0</code> to <code>v2.7.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>prettier/eslint-config-prettier</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"270\">2.7.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/cff31a21c1c6444ef640381c84a3b2356ce5ca25\"><code>cff31a2</code></a> eslint-config-prettier v2.7.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/5399175c37466747aae9d407021dffec2c169c8b\"><code>5399175</code></a> Improve no-tabs docs</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/816465cfa05c0607a828257540caf32b298be57d\"><code>816465c</code></a> Run tests on Node.js 8 as well</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/7afab86058c44e18f2e5d6bea898a10182d57f00\"><code>7afab86</code></a> Update dependencies</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/387e0f2c79d453f84ae7356d25431b6107871ba7\"><code>387e0f2</code></a> Add no-unexpected-multiline as a special rule (#&#8203;34)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/230d5957e48b7be138031ab2efdf07938afbc6b6\"><code>230d595</code></a> Remove unnecessary motivations for turning rules off</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/18a3d92abdace11497d1633ff36e5b4082c97e20\"><code>18a3d92</code></a> Add lines-around-comment as a special rule (#&#8203;33)</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
